{"meta":{"title":"Y4tacker's Blog","subtitle":"","description":"宁静致远，淡泊明志","author":"Y4tacker","url":"https://y4tacker.github.io","root":"/"},"pages":[{"title":"文章归档","date":"2022-02-02T14:20:49.594Z","updated":"2022-02-02T09:05:02.177Z","comments":true,"path":"archive.html","permalink":"https://y4tacker.github.io/archive.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"links","date":"2013-07-13T12:46:25.000Z","updated":"2022-02-02T09:08:29.273Z","comments":true,"path":"friend.html","permalink":"https://y4tacker.github.io/friend.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"about","date":"2022-02-02T13:39:44.000Z","updated":"2022-02-02T13:39:44.088Z","comments":true,"path":"about/index.html","permalink":"https://y4tacker.github.io/about/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"article","date":"2022-02-02T09:01:52.000Z","updated":"2022-02-02T09:01:52.965Z","comments":true,"path":"article/index.html","permalink":"https://y4tacker.github.io/article/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"分类","date":"2018-01-04T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-02-02T09:46:51.235Z","comments":true,"path":"categories/index.html","permalink":"https://y4tacker.github.io/categories/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"友情链接","date":"2022-02-02T09:46:05.000Z","updated":"2022-02-02T09:46:38.075Z","comments":true,"path":"link/index.html","permalink":"https://y4tacker.github.io/link/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"标签","date":"2018-01-04T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-02-02T09:47:00.241Z","comments":true,"path":"tags/index.html","permalink":"https://y4tacker.github.io/tags/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""}],"posts":[{"title":"Servlet的线程安全问题","slug":"year/2022/Servlet的线程安全问题","date":"2022-02-03T02:02:18.000Z","updated":"2022-02-03T02:37:34.533Z","comments":true,"path":"2022/02/03/year/2022/Servlet的线程安全问题/","link":"","permalink":"https://y4tacker.github.io/2022/02/03/year/2022/Servlet%E7%9A%84%E7%BA%BF%E7%A8%8B%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/","excerpt":"","text":"Servlet的线程安全问题引入首先看看这样的代码，有什么问题 这里既要求cmd不能包含Calculator又必须要包含Calculator，能做到吗，当然是可以的 Servlet的多线程机制Servlet实际上是一个单件，当我们第一次请求某个Servlet时，Servlet容器将会根据web.xml配置文件或者是注解实例化这个Servlet类，之后如果又有新的客户端请求该Servlet时，则一般不会再实例化该Servlet类，这说明了什么呢？简单来说，当多个用户一起访问时，得到的其实是同一个Servlet实例，这样的话，他们对实例的成员变量的修改其实会影响到别人，所以在开发的时候如果没有注意这个问题往往会有一些额安全问题，而往往Servlet的线程安全问题主要是由于实例变量使用不当而引起 因此我们再看上面的代码，很明显我们看到了这个status状态变量是实例变量","categories":[{"name":"Java","slug":"Java","permalink":"https://y4tacker.github.io/categories/Java/"}],"tags":[{"name":"Java","slug":"Java","permalink":"https://y4tacker.github.io/tags/Java/"},{"name":"Tomcat","slug":"Tomcat","permalink":"https://y4tacker.github.io/tags/Tomcat/"}]}],"categories":[{"name":"Java","slug":"Java","permalink":"https://y4tacker.github.io/categories/Java/"}],"tags":[{"name":"Java","slug":"Java","permalink":"https://y4tacker.github.io/tags/Java/"},{"name":"Tomcat","slug":"Tomcat","permalink":"https://y4tacker.github.io/tags/Tomcat/"}]}